Package prisonescape.game.screens

Class Summary
ActiveGame This class represents the current active game play which includes the map, HUD and pause menu
Credits Represents the Credits Screen
Help Represents the Help Screen showing you how to play the game with keyboard presses.
Loading Represents the Loading Screen just before going into the ActiveGame
MainMenu Represents the Main Menu Screen once the user has loaded the screen.
Minimap Represents the mini map view with 3 floor: Top floor, Bottom floor and Basement floor.
Pause Represents the Pause Menu screen when the user presses the "ESC" button while game play
Puzzle Represents the Puzzle Screen when completing mini-games
Splash Represents the splash screen with Prison Breakout logo when the user first loads the game.
